text: Diane M. Lanpher (born November 26, 1955) is an American Democratic politician. She is a member of the Vermont House of Representatives from the Addison's 3rd District, being first elected in 2008. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Buffalo, New York Category:Vermont Democrats Category:Members of the Vermont House of Representatives Category:Women state legislators in Vermont Category:21st- century American politicians Category:21st-century American women politicians
